      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 pt-4">
        <a href="/prezzi-e-abbonamenti" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full border border-white text-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-[#050322] transition-colors">
